<h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 32px 0 16px 0; line-height: 1.3;">Needs After Enrollment and Prior to Effective Date:</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #334155; margin: 0 0 12px 0;"><strong style="color: #111827;">Sedera:</strong> Any medical costs incurred after the enrollment date but prior to the start date are <strong style="color: #111827;">NOT shareable</strong>.</p>
<ul style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; padding-left: 24px; list-style-type: disc;">
